Z","msg":"快啲去最近嘅警察宿舍"},{"pid":"032ecd07a0153f6aa47b8424f0e2170fdd8a97ae","tid":1845661,"uid":291526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"大劣人真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f23ddf56bf1f76672ca9feab55fd0f0e39e7251","tid":1845661,"uid":69595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"推比青衣人睇"},{"pid":"9d4e4f0bf91c804ef78a7cf22499a9466f265a9b","tid":1845661,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3975e1f9b4f34ee98a97fe7324b8c75027327189","tid":1845661,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f93aadca7cb0346246c1376d42368d2e74898f5","tid":1845661,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DtKWpn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DtKWpn.jpg&h=a27c226a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色，是醫護常用顏色。不含任何色素，並容易發現污漬，適用於醫院最應保持潔淨的地方。除此之外，白色還代表純粹的善良和堅定的信念。<br />\n<br />\n當日，醫護們憑藉良心忠實履行自己的使命。今日，政權道德綁架他們這一份熱誠和信念。<br />\n<br />\n他們守護了我們生命和健康，但又誰能守護他們？<br />\n<br />\n全城白絲帶，支持醫護罷工。醫護不是condom，我們與醫護同行。<br />\n<br />\n#全城白絲帶 #撐醫護 #撐罷工 #封關口 #醫護非condom #與醫護同行<br />\n#香港金總 #HKFU #standwithmedics<br />\n<br />\n各位金融人都麻煩幫手填問卷，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️緊急⚠️⚠️<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工共同抗疫意見調查<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工總會欲以問卷方式詢問同業以工業行動共同抗疫的意願和意見，以制定有效方式向僱主及政府表達對僱員對於安全和健康的憂慮，全民共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態緊急，如策劃任何工業行動必需經過既定程序。故此是次問卷將於1月31日23:59截止。希望同業們積極參與此調查，讓金總能全面理解金融界僱主於防疫措施現況，以及會員和同業於共同抗疫的意願，以制定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtoVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=91bdce96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7</a><br />\n<br />\n原post傳送門：<br />\n［行動］［請置頂］全民白絲帶 罷工撐醫護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3abbdd360fe79c34baaca26459ad4236fedd14ac","tid":1845661,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824d9cdbe1ae7d489da24e1daa74490ef6e56784","tid":1845661,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff22b06ac6ca5c1f5a2fcb8d439bb1e569c16081","tid":1845661,"uid":135011,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"屌，我個fd補圖<br />\n係7仔見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55sf2ZX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55sf2ZX.jpg&h=8691bedc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:44:59.000Z","msg":"武漢人出沒注意"},{"pid":"55a5f921880c052a26851fc05229a57fe681f53f","tid":1845661,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"245c4d0e047bc4ff64c22b800a10f3b501fcbec5","tid":1845661,"uid":135011,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52m4M4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52m4M4h.jpg&h=283735dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T20:11:45.000Z","msg":"支那人真係個個d 樣都好似致命灣道中左幅射定亂輪生出黎d怪物咁撚樣"},{"pid":"e3954cb387c7df9b855a2abacc898f75d50c5cc0","tid":1845661,"uid":39860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"依d仆街最好見獲打獲，打到佢返支那"},{"pid":"5cb850ded247cf4a0ec3cba240990cb025610d88","tid":1845661,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"和記T9 隔離？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0723fc0a217e9971cae3d3a30f779912b63d93cb","tid":1845661,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:22:45.000Z","msg":"推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07edacce8b3ac5ed36b1b34e4ee1562b40318cb9","tid":1845661,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"帶菌者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1f7369156dde80ea7e1342aeb1b915a4177c64","tid":1845661,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n手足遠離果頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2Em2Bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2Em2Bw.jpg&h=565f5dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 基本上已可斷言武漢肺炎係來自武漢P4實驗室<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fnews.guo.offload.media%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25133703%2FBrief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=fb54df95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n1. 武漢沙士病毒好可能係人工<br />\n<br />\n-佢同2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒嘅E protein 100% 一樣 (相應嘅DNA 相似度都有225/228)，下一隻最接近嘅病毒已經只有低於95%一樣。<br />\n<br />\n病毒嘅基因複制同人類唔同；佢哋冇糾錯機制，發生變異機率相當大。即使E protein為保守序列，病毒品種相對不易產生變異，自然界中仍然非常唔可能有兩種冠狀病毒嘅E protein 完全一樣。SARS唔同亞種嘅E protein都有少量差別。<br />\n<br />\n-ORF8 基因通常病毒品種之間分別好大，2017浙江嗰隻嘅ORF8 同其他冠狀病毒最多只有60%似，但係同武漢沙士就有94.21%一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦推算武漢沙士病毒入侵人體嘅方式與SARS異常接近<br />\n<br />\nSARS入侵人體第一步，係病毒嘅S protein 痴落人體嘅ACE2 受體. 武漢沙士嘅S protein 整體上同SARS或者2017浙江嗰隻都唔似，但係真正痴落人體嗰部分就同沙士好似。最重要嗰五個氨基酸雖然同沙士有四個唔一樣，但係物理特性相似。電腦分析亦估算武漢沙士同人體ACE2 receptor 親和度非常高，只比SARS略低<br />\n<br />\n所以文章推斷為：有可能係有人參考沙士入侵呼吸道細胞ACE2 受體嘅方法，去改造2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒，再放出自然環境（如武漢市場）繁殖一段短時間"}]}